36:09.034 --> 36:11.093
-- I <i>told</i> Jenny <i>to come at 3:00.</i>
-- <i>Maybe she'll be fate.</i>

36:11.170 --> 36:14.401
-- She won't be late. -- She's
a pretty punctual porn star?

36:14.473 --> 36:16.305
