Take it easy.

36:16.375 --> 36:18.901
It cannot, it must not rain
at Indian Wells.

36:18.977 --> 36:20.911
Hey, I got a tee time with
David Duval, so get in line.

36:20.979 --> 36:23.846
Though, interestingly, it was a
rainstorm that ended our first fight.

36:23.916 --> 36:25.975
-- Interesting. -- All right,
back to being panicked.

36:26.051 --> 36:27.246
It cannot...

36:27.319 --> 36:29.720
it must not rain
at Indian Wells.

36:32.824 --> 36:33.985
Hello.

36:34.059 --> 36:35.390
-- Hello.
-- Hello.

36:35.460 --> 36:36.586
