to be totally upfront about who she is.

37:18.437 --> 37:21.236
-- VVhile still avoiding telling
Natalie who she is. -- Yes.

37:21.306 --> 37:22.603
-- Indian Wells.
-- Yes.

37:22.674 --> 37:24.073
-- Chance of rain.
-- Yes.

37:24.142 --> 37:26.133
-- Second-round coverage.
-- Yes.

37:26.211 --> 37:27.872
-- Jeremy Goodwin... totally screwed.
-- Yes.

37:27.946 --> 37:31.246
-- You like Draft Day, don't you? -- To
an admittedly psychotic extent, yes.

37:31.316 --> 37:32.579
See, and that's
another thing, too,

37:32.651 --> 37:34.551
'cause I'd like to be rooting
for rain at Indian Wells.

37:34.620 --> 37:35.883
I wanted to go
to the second round.

37:35.954 --> 37:37.285
-- But now?
-- Not so much.

37:37.356 --> 37:38.653
Jeremy, listen to me.

37:38.724 --> 37:40.715
Why don't you just
rip the bandage off,

37:40.792 --> 37:42.988
bite the bullet,
swallow hard, and tell her?

37:43.061 --> 37:46.622
You got to stop living in fear and start
rooting for rain at Indian VVells.

37:46.698 --> 37:47.631
-- Yes!
-- Good!

37:47.699 --> 37:49.224
-- That makes sense to me.
-- Good.

37:49.301 --> 37:50.894
-- That makes complete sense.
-- Yes.

37:50.969 --> 37:53.768
