-- And yet you stand here.

37:53.839 --> 37:56.240
Yes...okay.

37:56.308 --> 37:57.867
I will go.

37:59.711 --> 38:01.372
-- <i>It's Draft Day, Alyson.</i>
-- <i>Yeah.</i>

38:01.446 --> 38:02.880
-- Nothin' like it.
-- Yep.

38:02.948 --> 38:04.973
-- You know what Draft Day is?
-- <i>Nope.</i>

38:05.050 --> 38:05.983
