-- Okay.
-- I'm just saying...

38:14.893 --> 38:16.861
-- Natalie. Just the woman
I'm looking for. -- Hello.

38:16.928 --> 38:18.327
Coming out of
the mouth of anyone

38:18.397 --> 38:20.525
but the guy I just broke up
