38:20.599 --> 38:22.829
I broke up with you, but that
seems neither here nor there.

38:22.901 --> 38:24.062
Can I talk to you
a second?

38:24.136 --> 38:25.262
I broke up with you there,

38:25.337 --> 38:27.032
Mr. "Obviously has
a short-term memory loss

38:27.105 --> 38:28.402
"with a myriad
of other problems

38:28.473 --> 38:29.668
"which I won't even
