your saying that,

39:12.617 --> 39:14.915
and I appreciate your
being cool about it.

39:14.986 --> 39:17.250
Jeremy, please, I'm gonna walk out
of here, and I'm gonna break things,

39:17.322 --> 39:18.619
-- but for right now, in --
-- Yeah.

39:18.690 --> 39:20.658
You're an upfront guy,
Jeremy.

39:20.726 --> 39:22.717
You should stay that way.

39:22.794 --> 39:24.922
