40:47.479 --> 40:49.743
<i>I come to work. I do
my job. I do it well.</i>

40:49.815 --> 40:52.546
Maybe not well enough to
be 92nd on the list...

40:52.617 --> 40:54.915
-- <i>Oh, come on,</i> Danny.
-- <i>but I do it well enough.</i>

40:54.986 --> 40:56.385
-- You know what I'm talking about.
